    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Deseed</strong> the peppers (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dice</strong> into small, bite-size pieces&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Roughly</strong> chop (or tear) the basil, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 5,
